<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
      /* Theme Variables */
      :root {
        --bg-color: #ffffff;
        --text-color: #000000;
        --ul-bg-color: #f8f9fa;
        --ul-text-color: #000000;
      }

      /* Dark Mode Variables */
      .dark-mode {
        --bg-color: #212529;
        --text-color: #ffffff;
        --ul-bg-color: #333;
        --ul-text-color: #f8f9fa;
      }

      /* Apply Theme */
      body {
        background-color: var(--bg-color);
        color: var(--text-color);
        transition: background 0.3s ease-in-out, color 0.3s ease-in-out;
      }

      /* Theme Toggle Button */
      .theme-toggle-btn {
        position: absolute;
        top: 15px;
        right: 20px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        background: transparent;
        border: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <button id="themeToggleBtn" class="theme-toggle-btn">ðŸŒž</button>

    <div class="container mt-5">
      <h1>data-processing-strategies-renderer</h1>
      <div id="root" style="white-space: pre-wrap"></div>
    </div>

    <script>
      document.getElementById("root").innerHTML = `
<b>Different data format</b>         
  Pdf data
      render pdf in a pdf-viewer
      add metadata
  Json
  Db document 
  Local video 
  YouTube video 
  Udemy course 
  Topic, Memory maps, Questions, Tags, Node-relations
